Hereâ€™s a sneak peak at the <a href="https://github.com/JosephCrispell/reveal.js/blob/master/data-ethics-in-practice/index.html"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">index.html</code></a> that makes the above presentation:</p>

